      "features": [
        "Powerful Performance & 3 Speeds: Dominate your city commute with a high-torque 500W motor that reaches a top speed of 22 MPH. Featuring three adjustable 3 speed modes",
        "this electric scooter for adults allows you to seamlessly transition between crowded sidewalks and open bike lanes with total control.",
        "Extended Range: Travel further with our high-density battery system",
        "offering a range of up to 22 miles on a single 4 hours fast charge. Note: Actual range is influenced by rider weight",
        "ambient temperature",
        "and terrain conditions.",
        "Comfortable & Smooth Ride: This scooter features an upgraded front and rear suspension system that absorbs approximately 80% of vibrations on rough terrain",
        "increasing riding comfort.",
        "Maintenance-Free 10\" Solid Tires: Say goodbye to flat tires and air pumps. Our upgraded 10-inch solid tires are engineered with advanced shock-absorption technology to provide a smooth ride without the risk of punctures. These durable",
        "honeycomb-style tires ensure a stable journey over cracked asphalt and urban debris.",
        "Advanced Safety & Dual Braking: Ride with confidence thanks to the redundant safety of a responsive E-ABS electronic brake and a reinforced rear drum brake. Featuring a bright LED headlight and a reactive taillight for all-around visibility",
        "this foldable electric scooter ensures you remain seen.",
        "Smart App Control & Portability: Compaire your smartphone via bluetooth to lock your electric kick scooter",
        "customize cruise control",
        "and monitor live telemetry. The aerospace-grade aluminum frame folds in just 3 seconds",
        "making this lightweight scooter effortless to carry on public transit or store in car trunks."
